Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:19.74,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Sepertinya Ibu bisa urus\npenginapannya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:20.94,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:24.29,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Wah! Dekat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:34.20,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Hah? Apa? Suara apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.44,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Sambaran petir itu mungkin\Nmerubuhkan sesuatu di belakang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:40.27,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.30,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Akan kucek pintu belakang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.24,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:18.45,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah meminjamkan baju ganti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.51,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:23.71,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Cuma itu baju ukuranmu\nyang kupunya di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:27.11,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Aku beli jaket itu untuk\nlatihan membersihkan noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:30.15,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Ini tak masalah buatku.\NTerima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.30,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Hanya ini yang ada, tapi mau\nmakan dulu sebelum pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.03,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.86,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, tapi aku tak enak merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.08,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Oh, sama sekali tak merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:44.00,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Anggap saja ucapan terima kasih karena\nsudah menegakkan mesin cuci kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:08.31,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Tapi aku sungguh terbantu. \NTerima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:12.67,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa melakukan apa-apa\nkalau sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:13.82,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.13,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Enak! Ikan kering ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.96,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Rasanya sama dengan ikan\nyang kami sajikan di penginapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.84,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:36.09,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HCEC0B7&\3c&H9A501C&\shad0\fad(315,1)\move(1368,141,1311,141,148,2150)}Toko Oleh-Oleh
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:36.09,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HDCCCC2&\3c&H9A501C&\fs51\shad0\fad(315,1)\move(642,270,585,270,23,2150)}Toko Ikan Kering Atsuei
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.09,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Itu dari toko di dekat pantai,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.88,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Toko Ikan Kering Atsuei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.88,Default,Kyusho,0,0,0,,Toko Ikan Kering Atsuei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.60,Default,Kinme,0,0,0,,Pertama kali aku mencicipinya,\naku sangat takjub.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:47.35,Flashback,Nairo's Grandma,0,0,0,,Ini dia. Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.35,Flashback,Kinme,0,0,0,,Apa? Tapi aku masih\nsedang bekerja sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:20.56,Italics,Kyusho (M),0,0,0,,Dia pakai kacamata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:32.27,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\fs78\shad0\c&HE1F1FF&\3c&H77A3D9&\an9}Ibu\N{\c&H32515D&\3c&H6DD0E2&}Katanya\Nperingatan aktif\Nsampai matahari terbit
